{
  "stem": "9899.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we prepared when my father came from the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We would do the Kiddush and the prayers and have a traditional meal, a Shabbat meal that had the matzah [? kneydl ?] soup, the gefilte fish.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And of course, in those times everything was made from scratch.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You could not find anything packed or-- or in a jar.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "People would do them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And those times were nice and beautiful, and we looked forward to them very much so.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my little-- my older sister, of course, was always there with us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she contributed also quite a bit to these special ceremonies and understood very well.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were trained from a-- a very early age to differentiate the [? milchig, ?] the milk things, and the kosher-- and the meat--",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Meat.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--cutlery, and we were not allowed to mix them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we knew perfectly well what everything meant, all this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were educated in a religious way, so we were geared to being an Orthodox Jewish family.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in 1941, at the beginning of September, the Germans invaded Lwow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They came in, and they set up a command post.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were not many.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they started to interrogate all the people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They selected a few.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some of them-- them were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some of them were not.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they found, surprisingly, a strong collaboration in the Ukrainian people, who would, without any fear, and the Polish people, point out who the Jews were, where they lived.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And upon extracting a promise from the Germans that once the Jews would not be there any longer they would be able to take over their beautiful homes, they would point out to the Germans who they were, what were their names.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But still, we were a big number.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
